&lt;p&gt;We are looking for a high-energy, strategic &lt;strong&gt;Global&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;strong&gt;Sales Enablement Manager&lt;/strong&gt; to bridge the gap between our product, marketing, and sales teams. Your mission is simple: ensure our sales force has the tools, content, and training they need to turn &quot;maybe&quot; into &quot;yes&quot; more efficiently.&amp;nbsp; If you enjoy breaking down complex product features into winning talk tracks and thrive on seeing others hit their quotas, you’ll fit right in.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Key Responsibilities&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Training &amp;amp; Onboarding:&lt;/strong&gt; Design and deliver comprehensive onboarding programs to get new hires &quot;ramp-ready&quot; in record time.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
