&lt;p&gt;As MaxScale and its tests are written in C++, a &lt;strong&gt;good working knowledge of the language is expected&lt;/strong&gt;, along with a solid understanding of &lt;strong&gt;SQL&lt;/strong&gt;. In addition to testing, you will work closely&lt;br&gt;with support engineers and customers to verify and resolve reported problems, and assist in maintaining the automated build system.&lt;/p&gt;
