&lt;li&gt;Expert-level SQL - you think in joins, window functions, and CTEs; BigQuery and MariaDB experience strongly preferred&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong Python and/or JavaScript skills - comfortable building pipelines, internal tools, APIs, and automation; not just scripts&

