&lt;p&gt;We&#39;re hiring a &lt;strong&gt;Senior Data Scientist&lt;/strong&gt; with strong programming skills, a deep command of analytical methods, and the ability to turn complex data into clear business insights. You&#39;ll join a small, highly skilled team where your work has a direct impact on how the business operates and makes decisions.&lt;/p&gt;
